Sure, here are five example sentences that use the word "prihvatim" in different forms and positions, with the word highlighted with a star (*) and English translations in parentheses:

1. Kada *prihvatim* ovaj posao, obećavam da ću dati sve od sebe. (When I *accept* this job, I promise to give it my all.)
2. Molim te da mi *prihvatiš* izvinjenje zbog onog što sam uradio. (Please *accept* my apology for what I did.)
3. Nisam siguran da li ću *prihvatiti* taj predlog ili ne. (I'm not sure if I'll *accept* that proposal or not.)
4. Moram *prihvatiti* činjenicu da više ne mogu da se bavim sportom zbog povrede. (I have to *accept* the fact that I can no longer play sports due to injury.)
5. Da bih postao bolji čovek, moram *prihvatiti* svoje greške i pokušati da ih ispravim. (To become a better person, I must *accept* my mistakes and try to correct them.)